liza silabi za sauti lengwa zikitamkwa na mwalimu, mgeni mwalikwa au kutoka kwa vifaa vya kidijitali k.v. kinasasauti na rununu\", \"kutamka silabi alizozisikiliza ipasavyo akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kutamka ipasavyo maneno yenye silabi za sauti lengwa akiwa na wenzake\", \"kumwomba mzazi au mlezi kutumia kifaa cha kidijitali kama vile rununu ili kusikiliza matamshi ya sauti lengwa\"]','[\"Kwa ninini muhimu kutamka maneno ipasavyo?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',1,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34213,8543,'8.2','Kusoma: Kusoma kwa Ufasaha Sauti: (/j/, /r/, /p/, /f/, /v/, /sh/)',3,'[\"kutambua sauti lengwa katika kifungu chepesi cha hadithi\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha hadithi chenye sauti lengwa kwa kuzingatia matamshi bora\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha hadithi chenye sauti lengwa kwa sauti inayosikika\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha hadithi chenye sauti lengwa kwa kuzingatia kasi ifaayo\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha hadithi chenye sauti lengwa kwa kuzingatia ishara zifaazo\", \"kuchangamkia kusoma kwa ufasaha ili kufanikisha mawasiliano\"]','[\"kutambua sauti lengwa katika kifungu chepesi kuhusu suala lengwa akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha maneno chenye sauti lengwa kwa kuzingatia matamshi bora akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha maneno chenye sauti lengwa kwa kuzingatia kiwango kifaacho cha sauti akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha maneno chenye sauti lengwa kwa kuzingatia kasi ifaayo (maneno 25 kwa dakika na kwa kuzingatia viakifishi) akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kusoma hadithi kutoka kwenye kitabu, kifaa cha kidijitali, nk akishirikiana na wenzake, akizingatia matamshi bora, kasi ifaayo na kwa sauti inayosikika\", \"kumsomea mzazi au mlezi kifungu chepesi chenye sauti lengwa akizingatia matamshi bora, kasi ifaayo na kwa sauti inayosikika\"]','[\"Matamshi bora na sauti inayosikika yana umuhimu gani katika kusoma?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',2,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34214,8543,'8.3','Kuandika: Tahajia',3,'[\"kutambua tahajia sahihi katika sentensi\", \"kuandika sentensi tatu kuhusu suala lengwa akizingatia tahajia sahihi\", \"kuchangamkia matumizi ya tahajia sahihi katika uandishi wa sentensi\"]','[\"kutambua sentensi zinazohusu suala lengwa zenye tahajia sahihi kwa kutumia nyenzo kama vile: kadi za majina, mti maneno, kapu maneno, chati, kifungu au kifaa cha kidijitali\", \"kusoma sentensi zenye tahajia sahihi kuhusu suala lengwa\", \"kunakili sentensi zenye tahajia sahihi kuhusu suala lengwa kwenye daftari\", \"kutunga sentensi tatu sahihi kuhusu suala lengwa akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kuandika sentensi alizotunga kwa kuzingatia tahajia sahihi\", \"kusoma sentensi alizoandika pamoja na wenzake katika kikundi kisha wenzake wazitolee maoni\", \"kusahihisha sentensi alizoandika kwa kuzingatia tahajia\", \"Kumwonyesha mzazi au mlezi sentensi sahihi alizoandika ili apate maoni yake\"]','[\"Kwa nini ni muhimu kuyaandika maneno na sentensi kwa usahihi?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',3,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34215,8543,'8.4','Sarufi: Matumizi ya hiki na hivi',3,'[\"kutambua maneno hiki na hivi katika vifungu\", \"kusoma vifungu vinavyojumuisha maneno hiki na hivi ili kuonyeshea ifaavyo\", \"kutumia maneno hiki na hivi kuonyeshea vitu katika mazingira yake\", \"kuchangamkia matumizi ya hiki na hivi katika mawasiliano ya kila siku\"]','[\"kutambua hiki na hivi kwa kutumia nyenzo halisi, kadi za majina, kapu maneno au chati\", \"kusikiliza kifungu kinachohusu matumizi ya hiki na hivi katika kifaa cha kidijitali\", \"kusoma vifungu vinavyojumuisha hiki na hivi kisha abainishe matumizi ya hiki na hivi\", \"kuonyesha vitu mbalimbali kama vile vyakula na kuvitungia sentensi katika kikundi k.m. chakula hiki – vyakula hivi\", \"kumtungia mwenzake sentensi katika kikundi kwa kutumia hiki na hivi\", \"kutoa maoni kuhusu sentensi zilizotungwa na wenzake\", \"kukamilisha vifungu vyenye mapengo kwa kutumia hiki na hivi wakiwa wawiliwawili k.m. chakula (hiki, hii), vyakula (hivi, hizi)\"]','[\"Unajua majina yapi ya vitu vinavyoweza kuashiriwa kwa kutumia maneno hiki na hivi?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',4,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34216,8544,'9.1','Kusikiliza na Kuzungumza: Mazungumzo',3,'[\"kutambua suala lengwa ili azungumze kulihusu\", \"kuzungumza kuhusu suala lengwa akizingatia matamshi bora na ishara zifaazo\", \"kujieleza kwa ujasiri, kasi ifaayo na sauti inayosikika\", \"kuchangamkia mazungumzo na matamshi bora katika mawasiliano\"]','[\"kusikiliza mazungumzo mafupi kuhusu suala lengwa kutoka kwa mwalimu, mgeni mwalikwa au kifaa cha kidijitali\", \"kutazama video kuhusu mazungumzo yanayohusisha watoto\", \"kuwasilisha mazungumzo yake kwa wenzake katika kikundi kwa kuzingatia matamshi bora na ishara zifaazo\", \"kujieleza kwa ujasiri, kasi ifaayo na sauti inayosikika\", \"kusikiliza mazungumzo ya wenzake na kutoa maoni\", \"kushiriki katika mazungumzo kwa kuzingatia maagizo atakayopewa na mwalimu\", \"kujieleza kwa ujasiri ili kufanikisha mawasiliano akiwa na mzazi au mlezi jikoni\"]','[\"Unapenda kuzungumza kuhusu mambo gani ukiwa na wenzako?\", \"Unazingatia mambo gani unapozungumza mbele ya wenzako?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',1,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34217,8544,'9.2','Kusoma: Kusoma kwa Ufahamu Kifungu',3,'[\"kutambua msamiati kuhusu suala lengwa katika kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu\", \"kutabiri yatakayotokea katika kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu kwa kuzingatia picha\", \"kueleza ujumbe wa kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu\", \"kueleza mafunzo yanayotokana na kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu\", \"kuchangamkia kusoma vifungu vya ufahamu ili kuimarisha stadi ya kusoma\"]','[\"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu chenye maneno 23-30 na kutambua msamiati wa suala lengwa (k.v. kisu, kikombe, meko, sahani) akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kutumia msamiati wa suala lengwa ipasavyo katika mawasiliano\", \"kutabiri kitakachotokea katika hadithi akizingatia picha kwenye kifungu akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kuthibitisha utabiri wake kuhusu hadithi baada ya kuisoma\", \"kueleza ujumbe wa kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kueleza mafunzo yanayotokana na kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kumsomea mzazi au mlezi kifungu kuhusu suala lengwa\"]','[\"Je, tunaweza kujifunza mambo yapi kutokana na hadithi mbalimbali?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',2,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34218,8544,'9.3','Kuandika: Kifungu kutokana na Picha',3,'[\"kutazama picha na kutambua yaliyomo\", \"kuandika kifungu kuhusu yaliyomo katika picha\", \"kufurahia kuandika kifungu kutokana na yaliyomo katika picha\"]','[\"kutazama picha na kutambua wahusika, walipo wahusika na matendo yao akiwa peke\", \"kuandika daftarini au kwenye kifaa cha kidijitali kifungu cha sentensi mbili kutokana na picha aliyoitazama\", \"kumwonyesha mzazi au mlezi kifungu alichokiandika ili ampe maoni yake\"]','[\"Ni ujumbe upi unaoweza kuutoa kutokana na picha baada ya kuitazama?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',3,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34219,8544,'9.4','Sarufi: Matumizi ya Maneno Yanayoashiria Vitendo',3,'[\"kutambua maneno yanayoashiria vitendo katika kifungu na mawasiliano mbalimbali\", \"kusoma maneno yanayoashiria vitendo ili kujenga usomaji bora\", \"kutumia maneno yanayoashiria vitendo katika sentensi ipasavyo\", \"kufurahia kutumia maneno yanayoashiria vitendo katika mawasiliano\"]','[\"kutambua maneno yanayoashiria vitendo katika kadi maneno, mti maneno, chati au vifaa vya kidijitali\", \"kutaja mambo aliyofanya siku hiyo kama vile, kula, kuvaa, kupika, kuwasha, kuosha, pakua\", \"kuigiza vitendo k.m. kula, kunywa, keti, simama, nawa, choma\", \"kusoma maneno yanayoashiria vitendo ili kujenga usomaji bora\", \"kukamilisha sentensi akitumia maneno yanayoashiria vitendo\", \"kutunga sentensi zenye matumizi ya maneno yanayoashiria vitendo\", \"kumtungia mwenzake katika kikundi sentensi kwa kutumia maneno yanayoashiria vitendo\", \"kufanya zoezi la kujaza nafasi katika madaftari yao\"]','[\"Je, ni mambo yapi uliyofanya tangu jana?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',4,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34220,8545,'10.1','Kusikiliza na Kuzungumza: Matamshi Bora Sauti: (/ny/, /dh/, /th/, /ch/, /gh/, /ng/, /ng’/)',3,'[\"kutambua sauti lengwa katika kadi maneno\", \"kutamka sauti lengwa ipasavyo ili kuimarisha mazungumzo\", \"kutamka silabi za sauti lengwa ipasavyo\", \"kutamka ipasavyo maneno yenye silabi za sauti lengwa\", \"kuchangamkia nafasi ya matamshi bora katika mawasiliano\"]','[\"kushiriki katika kutambua sauti lengwa katika kadi maneno\", \"kutumia teknolojia (k.v. papaya) kusikiliza matamshi bora ya sauti lengwa\", \"kusikiliza mwalimu au mgeni mwalikwa akitamka sauti lengwa\", \"kutamka sauti pamoja na mwalimu\", \"kutamka sauti lengwa akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kutambua majina ya herufi zinazowakilisha sauti lengwa kwa kutumia kadi za herufi\", \"kutamka herufi za sauti lengwa akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kusikiliza silabi za sauti lengwa zikitamkwa na mwalimu, mgeni mwalikwa au kutoka kwa vifaa vya kidijitali k.v. kinasasauti na rununu\", \"kutamka silabi alizozisikiliza ipasavyo akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kutamka maneno yenye silabi za sauti lengwa ipasavyo\"]','[\"Ni majina yapi ya sauti /ny/,/dh/,/th/,/ch/, /gh/,/ng/, /ng’/unayojua kutamka?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',1,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34221,8545,'10.2','Kusoma: Kusoma kwa Ufasaha: Sauti: (/ny/, /dh/, /th/, /ch/, /gh/, /ng/, /ng’/)',3,'[\"kutambua sauti lengwa katika kifungu chepesi cha hadithi\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha hadithi chenye sauti lengwa kwa kuzingatia matamshi bora\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha hadithi chenye sauti lengwa kwa sauti inayosikika\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha hadithi chenye sauti lengwa kwa kuzingatia kasi ifaayo\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha hadithi chenye sauti lengwa kwa kuzingatia ishara zifaazo\", \"kuchangamkia kusoma kwa ufasaha ili kufanikisha mawasiliano\"]','[\"kutambua sauti lengwa katika kifungu chepesi kuhusu suala lengwa akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha maneno chenye sauti lengwa kuhusu suala lengwa kwa kuzingatia matamshi bora\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha maneno chenye sauti lengwa kwa kuzingatia kiwango kifaacho cha sauti\", \"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha maneno chenye suala lengwa (k.m kuhusu michezo mbalimbali, sehemu mbalimbali za barabara kwa kuzingatia kasi ifaayo (maneno 30 kwa dakika na kwa kizingatia viakifishi) akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kusoma hadithi kutoka kwenye kitabu, kifaa cha kidijtali, n.k akishirikiana na wenzake kwa kuzingatia matamshi bora, kasi ifaayo na kiwango kifaacho cha sauti\", \"kumsomea mzazi au mlezi kifungu chepesi cha hadithi chenye sauti lengwa akizingatia matamshi bora, kasi ifaayo na kiwango kifaacho cha sauti\"]','[\"Je, tunafaa kufanya nini tunapowasomea wengine kitabu kwa sauti?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',2,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34222,8545,'10.3','Kuandika: Kifungu kutokana na picha',3,'[\"kutazama picha na kutambua yaliyomo\", \"kuandika kifungu kuhusu yaliyomo katika picha\", \"kufurahia kuandika kifungu kutokana na yaliyomo katika picha\"]','[\"kutazama picha kuhusu suala lengwa na kutambua wahusika na matendo yao akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kueleza wenzake katika kikundi wahusika ni nani na wanafanya nini\", \"kuandika kifungu cha sentensi mbili kutokana na picha aliyoitazama\", \"kuwasomea wenzake sentensi alizoandika kuhusu picha\", \"kunakili sentensi alizoandika kwa kutumia kifaa cha kidijitali\", \"kuandika kifungu kwa kurejelea baadhi ya picha zinazopatikana nyumbani na sehemu mbalimbali za barabarani\"]','[\"Unapenda picha zinazohusu vitu gani?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',3,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34223,8545,'10.4','Sarufi: Vinyume vya Vitendo',3,'[\"kutambua vinyume vya vitendo mbalimbali katika kifungu chepesi\", \"kutumia majina ya vinyume vya vitendo katika mawasiliano\", \"kuchangamkia kutumia vitendo na vinyume vyake katika mawasiliano ya kila siku\"]','[\"kusoma maneno ya vitendo na vinyume vyake akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kutambua vinyume vya vitendo (kama vile, lala-amka; keti - simama; cheka - lia; enda - rudi; panda- shuka) katika kadi maneno, mti maneno, chati, kapu maneno au vifaa vya kidijitali\", \"kutumia vifaa vya kidijitali kusikiliza matumizi ya vinyume vya vitendo k.v. katika kifungu kinachosomwa\", \"kuigiza vinyume vya vitendo akiwa katika kikundi\", \"kushirikishwa kutaja majina ya vinyume vya vitendo\", \"kuandika vinyume vya vitendo\"]','[\"Je,vinyume gani vya vitendo unavyofanya kila siku?\"]','[]','[]','[]','[]',4,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34224,8546,'1.1','Pre-number activities',20,'[\"sort objects according to similar attributes in different situations\", \"match objects with similar attributes in the environment\", \"order objects according to given criteria in different situations\", \"create patterns of different sizes and shapes using real objects\", \"appreciate the use of sorting and grouping items in day-to-day activities\"]','[\"collect different types of safe objects from the immediate environment\", \"group objects according to attributes such as size, colour, use, shape, and texture\", \"in teams, pair objects with similar attributes such as size, colour, use, shape, and texture\", \"arrange objects according to size from smallest to biggest and from biggest to smallest\", \"make patterns of different shapes and sizes using real objects\", \"assist in arranging items like fruits and cereals, for example beans, maize, and rice according to size, colour, shape and storage at home\"]','[\"How can we group objects?\", \"How can we arrange objects?\"]','[\"Creativity: learner makes patterns of different shapes and sizes using real objects.\", \"Self-efficacy: learner assists in arranging items according to size, colour, shape, and storage at home.\"]','[\"Unity: in teams, learner matches objects according to size, colour, and shape.\", \"Responsibility: learner assists in arranging items according to size, colour, shape, and storage at home.\"]','[\"Safety: learner observes safety as they collect objects from the immediate environment.\", \"Social Cohesion: learner works with peers as they pair and match objects according to size, colour and shape.\"]','[\"The learner can relate the skills used in creating patterns to the concept of patterns in Creative Activities.\"]',1,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34225,8546,'1.2','Whole Numbers',25,'[\"count numbers forward up to 50\", \"count numbers backward from 30\", \"represent numbers 1 to 30 using concrete objects\", \"read and write numbers 1 to 50 in symbols\", \"read and write numbers 1 to 10 in words\", \"identify missing numbers in number patterns up to 20\", \"appreciate number patterns by creating and extending patterns during play activities\"]','[\"collect concrete objects from the immediate environment to use in counting activities\", \"count by 1’s and 2’s up to 20 starting from any point using concrete objects such as number cards, as well as body parts\", \"take turns in counting numbers forward up to 50\", \"count numbers backward from 30\", \"play games that involve representing numbers 1 to 30 using concrete objects\", \"read and write numbers 1 to 50 in symbols\", \"practise writing numbers 1 to 10 in words\", \"fill in missing numbers in number patterns up to 20\", \"create patterns with numbers up to 20 and share them with other groups\", \"play games involving whole numbers using digital devices or other resources\"]','[\"In what ways can we count from 1 to 20?\"]','[\"Digital Literacy: learner uses digital devices to play games involving numbers 1 to 50.\", \"Creativity: learner creates patterns with numbers up to 20.\"]','[\"Respect: learner appreciates peers as they take turns in counting numbers forward up to 50.\"]','[\"Social Cohesion: learner takes turns counting numbers forward up to 50.\", \"Environmental Safety: learner observes safety when collecting concrete objects from the immediate environment.\"]','[\"The learner can relate the skills used in the concept of reading and writing numbers in words and symbols to functional reading and writing in English Language Activities.\", \"The learner can relate the skills used in creating number patterns to the concept of patterns in Creative Activities.\"]',2,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34226,8546,'1.3','Addition',25,'[\"model addition as putting objects together\", \"use \' +\' and \' =\' signs in writing addition statements\", \"add 2 single-digit numbers in different situations\", \"add 3 single-digit numbers in different contexts\", \"add a 2-digit number to a 1-digit number without regrouping with sum not exceeding 50\", \"work out missing numbers in patterns involving the addition of whole numbers up to 50\", \"play games involving addition using digital devices or other resources\"]','[\"safely put two groups of objects together and count to get the total\", \"create scenarios where addition is relevant i.e there are two apples on the table, add three more, how many apples are there\", \"use flashcards with addition problems to practise quick recall of basic facts\", \"roll dice to add numbers together\", \"use number cards or abacus to add a 2-digit number to a 1-digit number without regrouping horizontally and vertically with a sum not exceeding 50\", \"make number patterns involving addition with numbers up to 50\", \"play games involving addition using digital devices and other resources\"]','[\"How can you add a 2-digit number to a 1-digit number?\"]','[\"Creativity: learner makes number patterns involving addition.\", \"Collaboration: learner plays games involving addition with peers.\"]','[\"Social Justice: learner accommodates others as they play games involving addition.\"]','[\"Safety Issues: learner safely puts two groups of objects together and counts to get the total.\", \"Creative thinking: learner creatively makes number patterns involving addition with numbers up to 50.\"]','[\"The learner can relate the skills used in writing addition sentences to functional writing in English Language Activities.\"]',3,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34227,8546,'1.4','Subtraction',20,'[\"model subtraction as \'taking away\' using concrete objects\", \"use the \' - \' and \'=\'signs in writing subtraction sentences\", \"subtract single digit numbers\", \"subtract a 1-digit number from a 2-digit number without regrouping\", \"work out missing numbers in patterns involving subtraction of whole numbers up to 50\", \"play games involving subtraction using digital devices and other resources\"]','[\"model subtraction using concrete objects\", \"use \' - \' and \'=\' signs in writing subtraction sentences\", \"subtract by counting backward\", \"subtract using concrete objects\", \"make subtraction sentences related to basic addition facts\", \"use number cards or charts safely to work out subtraction of a 1-digit number from a 2-digit number\", \"work with peers to create patterns involving subtraction\"]','[\"How do you subtract a one- digit number from a two-digit number?\"]','[\"Learning to Learn: learner learns the subtraction of numbers by counting backwards.\", \"Creativity: learner creates patterns involving subtraction.\"]','[\"Responsibility: learner takes care of concrete objects used in subtraction.\", \"Unity: learner shares number cards or charts as they work out subtraction.\"]','[\"Social Cohesion: learner works with peers to create patterns involving subtraction.\", \"Critical thinking: learner works out subtraction by counting backward.\"]','[\"The learner can relate the skills of writing subtraction sentences to functional writing in English Language Activities.\"]',4,'2025-12-07 19:11:19',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34228,8547,'2.1','Length',10,'[\"collect objects of different lengths from the immediate environment\", \"compare the length of objects using longer than, shorter than, and 