unga sentensi katika hali ya mazoea na hali timilifu ili wenzake waweze kuisoma na kutathmini usahihi wake\"]','[\"Je, wewe hufanya shughuli gani kila siku?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake kubadilisha sentensi kutoka hali moja hadi nyingine\", \"Ubunifu: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi katika hali ya mazoea na hali timilifu\", \"Hamu ya ujifunzaji: mwanafunzi anapoendelea kutunga sentensi katika hali ya mazoea na hali timilifu\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia kifaa cha kidijitali kuandika sentensi\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapojifunza kuthamini maoni ya wengine katika shughuli za somo\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake katika kutunga sentensi\"]','[\"Kujithamini: anapotunga sentensi sahihi na kuzitumia kujieleza\", \"Tamaduni hasi za kijamii: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi zinazohusiana na kudhibiti itikadi za kidini na za kijamii\"]','[\"English: Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha matumizi ifaayo ya nyakati na hali na somo la English kwa sababu somo hili hufundisha matumizi ya nyakati na hali\"]',4,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34880,8694,'11.1.1','Masimulizi',2,'[\"Kusikiliza masimulizi kwa kuzingatia ujumbe\", \"Kusimulia tungo mbele ya wenzake kwa kuzingatia mada, ubunifu na usanifu wa lugha\", \"Kutumia ishara zifaazo kuimarisha masimulizi yake\", \"Kuchangamkia masimulizi katika mazingira mbalimbali\"]','[\"Kusikiliza masimulizi yakitolewa na mgeni mwalikwa, mwalimu, mwanafunzi mwenzake au kutokana na vifaa vya kidijitali\", \"Kubuni masimulizi yanayohusiana na mada husika kwa kutazama picha, michoro au kujadiliana na wenzake\", \"Kutoa masimulizi kuhusu mada (k.v. Jinsi ya kuwekeza na faida za uwekezaji)\", \"Kutumia ishara za mwili zifaazo k.v. ishara za uso, za mikono na mabega ili kuimarisha masimulizi yake\", \"Kujadiliana na wenzake kuhusu ubora wa masimulizi aliyosikiliza\"]','[\"Je, ni nini unachozingatia katika kutoa masimulizi?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anapojadili kuhusu ubora wa masimulizi na wenzake\", \"Ubunifu: mwanafunzi anapotunga na kusimulia visa mbalimbali\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anaposimulia visa mbele ya wenzake\"]','[\"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapotoa masimulizi kuhusu uwekezaji\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anapojadiliana na wenzake ubora wa masimulizi aliyosikiliza\"]','[\"Elimu ya fedha: mwanafunzi anaposimulia kuhusu uwekezaji\", \"Mshikamano wa kijamii na kitaifa: mwanafunzi anposimulia kuhusu uwekezaji akiwa na wenzake\"]','[\"English: Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha kusikiliza na kusimulia masimulizi na somo la English kwa sababu somo hili hufundisha masimulizi\"]',1,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34881,8694,'11.2.1','Kusoma kwa Ufasaha',2,'[\"Kutambua vipengele vya kuzingatia katika kusoma kwa ufasaha\", \"Kusoma kifungu kwa kuzingatia matamshi bora\", \"Kusoma kifungu kwa kasi ifaayo\", \"Kusoma kifungu kwa kutumia sauti ipasavyo\", \"Kusoma kifungu kwa kuambatanisha ishara zifaazo\", \"Kuchangamkia kusoma kifungu kwa kuzingatia vipengele vya usomaji\"]','[\"Kujadiliana na wenzake vipengele vya kuzingatia katika kusoma makala kwa ufasaha\", \"Kutazama vielelezo vya video vinavyoonyesha usomaji fasaha wa makala (k.v. hotuba, habari,) akiwa peke yake au na wenzake\", \"Kusoma kifungu akizingatia matamshi bora\", \"Kusoma kifungu cha hadithi kuhusu suala lengwa kwa kuzingatia kasi ifaayo (maneno sahihi yasiyopungua 75 kwa dakika) ili wenzake wamtolee maoni\", \"Kusoma kifungu akizingatia sauti ifaayo (k.v. kiwango cha sauti na kiimbo)\", \"Kusoma kifungu kwa kuambatanisha ishara zifaazo panapofaa (k.v. ishara za uso na mikono zinazozingatia tamaduni)\"]','[\"Unaposoma kifungu ni mambo yapi unayozingatia ili kusoma ifaavyo?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anapowasomea wenzake kifungu\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anaposoma kifungu mbele ya wenzake\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anaposikiliza kwa makini wenzake wakisoma kifungu\", \"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anaposoma kifungu kwa ukamilifu\"]','[\"Kujithamini: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki kikamilifu shughuli za vikundi na kuzikamilisha\"]','[\"English: Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha kusoma kwa ufasaha na somo la English kwa sababu somo hili hufundisha kusoma kwa ufasaha\"]',2,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34882,8694,'11.3.1','Baruapepe',2,'[\"Kutambua baruapepe kwa kuzingatia muundo wake\", \"Kuandika baruapepe kwa kuzingatia ujumbe, muundo na mtindo\", \"Kuchangamkia uandishi wa baruapepe katika mawasiliano\"]','[\"Kutambua muundo wa baruapepe kwa kurejelea kielelezo chake kilichochapishwa au kwenye tarakilishi\", \"Kujadili na wenzake sehemu mbalimbali za baruapepe kama vile anwanipepe ya mtumaji, anwanipepe ya mpokeaji, mada ya baruapepe, mtajo, mwili, hitimisho na jina la mwandishi/mtumaji\", \"Kuandika baruapepe kwa rafiki, mzazi, mwalimu akishirikiana na wenzake kwa kutumia tarakilishi akizingatia muundo wa uandishi wa baruapepe\", \"Kutuma baruapepe aliyoiandika kwa mpokeaji\", \"Kujadiliana na wenzake kuhusu umuhimu wa baruapepe katika mawasiliano\"]','[\"Unazingatia vipengele gani unapoandika baruapepe?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anapoandika na kutuma baruapepe\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia tarakilishi kuandika na kutuma baruapepe\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapotuma baruapepe kwa mpokeaji\"]','[\"Upendo: mwanafunzi anapotuma baruapepe kwa wazazi au marafiki kuwajulia hali\", \"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapozingatia maoni ya wengine wakati wa mjadala\", \"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapoandika baruapepe akizingatia muundo wa kuiandika\"]','[\"Mawasiliano faafu: mwanafunzi anapotumia baruapepe kuwasiliana\", \"Elimu ya maendeleo endelevu: mwanafunzi anapotumia tarakilishi na mtandao kuwasiliana\"]','[\"English: Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha kutambua na kuandika baruapepe kwa kutumia tarakilishi na somo la English kwa sababu somo hili hufundisha utambuzi na uandishi wa baruapepe kwa kutumia tarakilishi\"]',3,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34883,8694,'11.4.1','Ukanushaji - Viambishi vya wakati li, na na ta',3,'[\"Kutambua viambishi vya wakati na nafsi katika sentensi\", \"Kukanusha viambishi vya nafsi na wakati katika sentensi kwa usahihi\", \"Kutunga sentensi sahihi zenye viambishi vya nafsi na wakati na kuzikanusha\", \"Kufurahia ukanushaji wa viambishi vya nafsi na wakati katika sentensi\"]','[\"Kutambua viambishi vya nafsi hali ya mazoea na timilifu katika vitenzi kwa kuvipigia mistari kwenye vitabu au kuvikolezea wino kwenye tarakilishi\", \"Kutambua viambishi vya wakati li, na na ta katika hali yakinishi na ku, ta, si, ha katika hali kanushi akiwa na wenzake\", \"Kusoma sentensi zenye viambishi lengwa kwenye vitabu au tarakilishi katika hali yakinishi na kanushi\", \"Kukanusha sentensi akizingatia nafsi na nyakati kwenye daftari au kwa kutumia tarakilishi akiwa peke yake au na wenzake\", \"Kusikiliza au kutazama vipindi vya ukanushaji wa nafsi na wakati kupitia vifaa vya kidijitali akiwa peke yake au katika kikundi\"]','[\"Viambishi vya nafsi katika vitenzi ni vipi?\", \"Unatumia viambishi gani wakati wa kukanusha vitenzi?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anapokanusha sentensi akizingatia viambishi vya nyakati husika akiwa na wenzake\", \"Uwazaji kina na utatuzi wa matatizo: mwanafunzi anapokanusha sentensi akizingatia viambishi vya nyakati husika\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia vifaa vya kidijitali kusikiliza au kutazama vipindi vya ukanushaji\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi katika hali Kanushi akizingatia viambishi vya nyakati li, na na ta\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapothamini wenzake wanapotambua viambishi vya wakati li, na na ta katika hali yakinishi na ku, ta, si, ha katika hali kanushi\", \"Uadilifu: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi sahihi kuhusu uwekezaji\"]','[\"Kujithamini: mwanafunzi anakuza uwezo wa kukabili au kukataa mambo mbalimbali maishani\", \"Umaskini: mwanafunzi anapotumia viambishi vya nafsi na vya wakati katika sentensi zinazolenga suala lengwa\"]','[\"English: Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha kukanusha kwa kutumia viambishi vya wakati na somo la English kwa sababu somo hili hufundisha ukanushaji na dhana ya viambishi\"]',4,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34884,8694,'11.4.2','Ukubwa na Udogo wa Nomino (m-)',2,'[\"Kutambua nomino zinazoanza kwa herufi m- na zenye mzizi wa silabi mbili\", \"Kutambua nomino zinazoanza kwa herufi m- katika hali ya ukubwa na udogo\", \"Kubadilisha nomino katika hali ya wastani kuwa katika hali ya ukubwa na udogo\", \"Kutumia nomino zinazoanza kwa herufi m- katika hali ya ukubwa na udogo kwenye sentensi\", \"Kufurahia kutumia nomino katika hali ya ukubwa na udogo kwa usahihi ili kuimarisha mawasiliano\"]','[\"Kutambua nomino zinazoanza kwa herufi m- na zenye mzizi wa silabi mbili (k.m mtoto, mlango, mkate na mlima) kwenye chati, ubao, mti maneno, kapu la maneno au kifaa cha kidijitali\", \"Kutambua nomino zinazoanza kwa herufi m- na zenye mzizi wa silabi mbili katika ukubwa na udogo (k.v. mtoto (toto- kitoto), mlango (lango - kilango), mkate (kate- kikate)\", \"Kushiriki katika vikundi kubadilisha nomino kutoka hali ya wastani hadi hali ya ukubwa na udogo\", \"Kushiriki katika mchezo wa vikundi ambapo kikundi kimoja kitataja wastani wa nomino na kingine kutaja ukubwa na udogo wa nomino hiyo\", \"Kupewa orodha ya nomino katika hali ya ukubwa na orodha nyingine ya nomino katika hali ya udogo kwenye tarakilishi ili aziburure kuziambatanisha\", \"Kutunga sentensi zinazorejelea nomino lengwa katika ukubwa na udogo akiwa peke yake au kwenye vikundi\"]','[\"Ni nomino gani unazoweza kutaja ukubwa wake?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki katika mchezo wa vikundi ambapo kikundi kimoja kitataja wastani wa nomino na kingine kutaja ukubwa na udogo wa nomino hiyo\", \"Ubunifu: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi katika hali ya ukubwa na udogo\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia tarakilishi kutambua na kuambatanisha nomino katika hali ya wastani, ukubwa na udogo\"]','[\"Upendo: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki katika vikundi kubadilisha nomino kutoka hali ya wastani hadi hali ya ukubwa na udogo\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi katika ukubwa na udogo akiwa kwenye vikundi\"]','[\"Elimu ya kifedha: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi za ukubwa na udogo kuhusu uwekezaji\"]','[\"English: Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha kutambua na kubadilisha nomino katika ukubwa na udogo na somo la English kwa sababu somo hili hufundisha ukubwa na udogo wa nomino\"]',5,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34885,8694,'11.4.3','Ukubwa na Udogo wa Nomino (n-)',2,'[\"Kutambua nomino zinazoanza kwa herufi n- ili kuzitofautisha na nomino nyingine\", \"Kutambua nomino zinazoanza kwa herufi n- katika hali ya ukubwa na udogo\", \"Kubadilisha nomino katika hali wastani kuwa katika hali ya ukubwa na udogo\", \"Kutumia nomino katika hali ya ukubwa na udogo kwenye sentensi ili kuimarisha mawasiliano\", \"Kufurahia kutumia nomino katika hali ya ukubwa na udogo kwa usahihi ili kuimarisha mawasiliano\"]','[\"Kutambua nomino zinazoanza kwa herufi n- kwenye chati, ubao, mti maneno, kapu la maneno au kifaa cha kidijitali\", \"Kushiriki katika vikundi kubadilisha nomino kutoka hali ya wastani hadi hali ya ukubwa na udogo\", \"Kushiriki katika mchezo wa vikundi ambapo kikundi kimoja kitataja wastani wa nomino, kingine ukubwa na kingine kutaja udogo wa nomino hiyo\", \"Kupewa orodha ya nomino katika hali ya ukubwa na orodha nyingine ya nomino katika hali ya udogo kwenye tarakilishi ili aziburure kuziambatanisha\", \"Kutunga sentensi zinazorejelea nomino lengwa katika ukubwa na udogo akiwa peke yake au kwenye vikundi\"]','[\"Ni nomino gani unazoweza kutaja udogo wake?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki katika mchezo wa vikundi ambapo kikundi kimoja kitataja wastani wa nomino na kingine kutaja ukubwa na udogo wa nomino hiyo\", \"Ubunifu: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi katika hali ya ukubwa na udogo\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia tarakilishi kutambua na kuambatanisha nomino katika hali ya wastani, ukubwa na udogo\"]','[\"Upendo: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki katika vikundi kubadilisha nomino kutoka hali ya wastani hadi hali ya ukubwa na udogo\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi katika ukubwa na udogo akiwa kwenye vikundi\"]','[\"Elimu ya kifedha: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi za ukubwa na udogo kuhusu uwekezaji\"]','[\"English: Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha kutambua na kubadilisha nomino katika ukubwa na udogo na somo la English kwa sababu somo hili hufundisha ukubwa na udogo wa nomino\"]',6,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34886,8695,'1.1','Whole Numbers',20,'[\"Use place value and total value of digits up to hundreds of thousands in different situations\", \"Read and write numbers up to tens of thousands in words in different situations\", \"Order numbers up to tens of thousands in different situations\", \"Round off numbers up to tens of thousands to the nearest hundred and thousand in different situations\", \"Apply divisibility tests of 2, 5 and 10 in real-life situations\", \"Determine Highest Common Factor (HCF) and Greatest Common Divisor (GCD) in different situations\", \"Determine Least Common Multiple (LCM) in real-life situations\", \"Appreciate use of whole numbers in real-life situations\"]','[\"Identify place value of digits up to hundreds of thousands using place value apparatus or place value charts\", \"Identify total value of digits up to hundreds of thousands using place value charts\", \"Read numbers up to hundreds of thousands in symbols from number charts or cards\", \"Read and write numbers up to tens of thousands in words from number charts or cards\", \"Arrange numbers up to tens of thousands in increasing and decreasing order\", \"Discuss and round off numbers up to tens of thousands to the nearest hundred and thousand using number cards and share with other groups\", \"Carry out the divisibility test for 2, 5 and 10 and come up with divisibility rules\", \"Express numbers in terms of their factors then identify the common factors\", \"Express the multiples of numbers and identify multiples of the common multiples as well as the least common multiples\", \"Play games involving numbers using digital devices or other resources\"]','[\"Where can we use ordering of numbers in real life?\", \"Why should we round off numbers?\"]','[\"Critical thinking and problem solving: learner orders and rounds off numbers\", \"Learning to learn: learner reads and writes numbers, computing the total values of numbers\"]','[\"Unity: learner works with peers in identifying factors, divisors and multiples of numbers to enhance unity\"]','[\"Safety: learner observes safety precautions while handling apparatus for carrying out operations on numbers\"]','[\"The learner is able to relate whole numbers to reading and writing numbers symbols and words in languages\"]',1,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34887,8695,'1.2','Addition',6,'[\"Add up to three 6-digit numbers without regrouping up to a sum not exceeding 1,000,000 in different situations\", \"Add up to two 6-digit numbers with double regrouping with the sum not exceeding 1,000,000 in different situations\", \"Estimate sum by rounding off the addends to the nearest hundred and thousand in different situations\", \"Create patterns involving the addition of numbers up to a sum of 1,000,000 in real-life situations\", \"Appreciate use of the addition of whole numbers in real-life situations\"]','[\"Work out the sum of three 6-digit numbers without regrouping up to 1,000,000 using place charts or any other resource\", \"Collaborate with others to work out the sum of two 6-digit numbers with double regrouping with the number not more than 1,000,000 using place value apparatus or any other resource\", \"Estimate sums by rounding off the addends to the nearest hundred and thousand\", \"Come up with patterns involving addition of numbers up to a sum of 1,000,000\", \"Play games involving addition of numbers using digital devices and other resources\"]','[\"How can you estimate the sum of given numbers?\", \"How can you create patterns in addition?\"]','[\"Creativity and imagination: learner makes number patterns involving addition\", \"Digital literacy: learner uses digital devices and other resources to learn and play games in addition concept development\"]','[\"Unity: learner collaborates with others to work out the sum of two 6-digit numbers\", \"Responsibility: learner takes roles individually to achieve common solutions in addition of numbers\"]','[\"Social cohesion: learner works with peers in using digital resources for learning the addition of numbers\"]','[\"The learner is able to relate the concept of addition to value addition in Agriculture and Nutrition\"]',2,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34888,8695,'1.3','Subtraction',6,'[\"Subtract up to two 6-digit numbers without regrouping in real-life situations\", \"Subtract up to two 6-digit numbers with regrouping in different situations\", \"Estimate difference by rounding off the minuend and subtrahend to the nearest hundred and thousand in different situations\", \"Perform combined operations involving addition and subtraction in different situations\", \"Create patterns involving subtraction from up to 1,000,000 in different situations\", \"Appreciate subtraction of numbers in real-life situations\"]','[\"Work with peers to subtract up to two 6-digit numbers without regrouping using place value apparatus\", \"Discuss and work out subtraction of up to two 6-digit numbers with regrouping using place value apparatus\", \"Team up with peers to estimate difference by rounding off the minuend and subtrahend to the nearest hundred and thousand using a number line\", \"Work out questions involving addition and subtraction\", \"Generate patterns involving subtraction of whole numbers from up to 1,000,000\", \"Play games involving subtraction of numbers using digital devices and other resources\"]','[\"How do you estimate difference to the nearest hundred?\", \"How can you create number patterns involving subtraction?\"]','[\"Creativity and imagination: learner creates number patterns involving subtraction\", \"Self-efficacy: learner reports the group\'s discussion to others in carrying out the various subtraction skills\"]','[\"Unity: learner harmoniously works with peers to subtract of up to 6-digit numbers without regrouping using place value apparatus\"]','[\"Social cohesion: learner carries out the group work in estimation of differences\"]','[\"The learner is able to relate the concept of subtraction to the decrease of economic resources in Social Studies\"]',3,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34889,8695,'1.4','Multiplication',6,'[\"Multiply up to a 3-digit number by up to a 2-digit number in real-life situations\", \"Estimate product by rounding off numbers to the nearest ten in different situations\", \"Make patterns involving multiplication of numbers with product not exceeding 1000 in different situations\", \"Appreciate use of multiplication in real life\"]','[\"Work out multiplication of up to a 3-digit number by up to a 2-digit number using different methods\", \"Round off numbers to the nearest tens then get their product using compatibility of numbers or own strategies\", \"Team up with peers to create patterns involving multiplication of numbers with products not exceeding 1000\", \"Play games involving multiplication of whole numbers using digital devices and other resources\"]','[\"Where can multiplication be used in real life?\", \"How can you form patterns involving multiplication?\"]','[\"Communication and collaboration: learner works with peers to make patterns involving multiplication\", \"Learning to learn: learner explores other methods of working out products of numbers\"]','[\"Unity: learner teams up with peers to create patterns involving multiplication of numbers with products not exceeding 1000\"]','[\"Self-awareness: learner discovers own strategies in multiplication and estimation of products of numbers\"]','[\"The learner is able to relate the concept of multiplication to sowing tiny seeds gardening skills in Agriculture and Nutrition\"]',4,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34890,8695,'1.5','Division',6,'[\"Divide up to a 3-digit number by up to a 2-digit number where the dividend is greater than the divisor in real life\", \"Apply the relationship between multiplication and division in different situations\", \"Divide up to 3-digit number by 1000 in different situations\", \"Estimate quotients by rounding off the dividend and divisor to the nearest ten in real-life situations\", \"Perform combined operations involving addition, subtraction, multiplication and division of whole numbers in different situations\", \"Appreciate use of division of whole numbers in real-life situations\"]','[\"Work out division of up to a 3-digit number by up to a 2-digit number where the dividend is greater than the divisor using long and short form\", \"Collaborate to show that multiplication is the opposite of division\", \"Estimate quotients by rounding off the dividend and divisor to the nearest ten\", \"Work out questions involving addition, subtraction, multiplication and division\", \"Create number games and puzzles involving division\", \"Share digital resources or other resources with peers while playing games involving the division of whole numbers\"]','[\"Where is division used in real life?\", \"How can we estimate quotients?\"]','[\"Creativity and Imagination: learner creates number games and puzzles involving division\", \"Digital Literacy: learner plays digital games involving divisions\"]','[\"Social Justice: learner shares digital resources or other resources with peers while playing games involving the division of whole numbers\"]','[\"Self-esteem: learner discovers strategies of working out division and creates number games and puzzles\"]','[\"The learner is able to relate the concept of division to the allocation and sharing in Agriculture\"]',5,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34891,8695,'1.6','Fractions',8,'[\"Simplify fractions in different situations\", \"Compare fractions in different situations\", \"Order fractions with denominators not exceeding 12 in different situations\", \"Add two fractions with the same denominator in different situations\", \"Subtract two fractions with the same denominator in different situations\", \"Add two fractions with one renaming in different situations\", \"Subtract two fractions with one renaming in different situations\", \"Appreciate the use of fractions in real life\"]','[\"Identify equivalent fractions using a fraction board or chart\", \"Represent equivalent fractions using real objects\", \"Use charts or others resources to express fractions in their simplest forms\", \"Arrange given fractions in increasing or decreasing order using different methods\", \"Add fractions with the same denominator using paper cut-outs, real objects or other resources\", \"Subtract two fractions with the same denominator using paper cut-outs, number lines, real objects, or other resources\", \"Carry out addition of two fractions by renaming one fraction using equivalent fractions\", \"Carry out subtraction of two fractions by renaming one fraction using equivalent fractions\"]','[\"Why can we order fractions in real life?\", \"Where are fractions used in real life?\"]','[\"Learning to learn: learner orders, compares and simplifies fractions\", \"Digital Literacy: learner plays digital games involving fractions\"]','[\"Responsibility: learner prepares paper cut-outs and collects concrete objects for comparing fractions\"]','[\"Safety: learner observes safety precautions while collecting concrete objects for learning\"]','[\"The learner is able to relate the concept of fractions to mixtures in Science and Technology\"]',6,'2025-12-07 19:11:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),(34892,8695,'1.7','Decimals',6,'[\"Identify plac