otumika katika mawaidha\", \"kujadili na wenzake ishara zinazotumika katika mawaidha\", \"kutoa mawaidha kwa kuzingatia vipengele vya lugha na ishara zinazotumika\", \"kumsikiliza mzazi au mlezi wake akitoa mawaidha na kuzingatia vipengele na ishara alizotumia\"]','[\"Unazingatia nini unapowasilisha mawaidha?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake katika kujadili vipengele vya lugha vinavyotumika katika mawaidha\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia vifaa vya kidijitali kutafuta mawaidha\", \"Ubunifu: mwanafunzi anapotoa mawaidha kwa kutumia vipengele vya lugha na ishara ipasavyo\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapotoa mawaidha kwa ukakamavu mbele ya wenzake\", \"Hamu ya ujifunzaji: mwanafunzi anapomsikiliza mzazi au mlezi wake akitoa mawaidha\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapothamini maoni ya wenzake katika kazi ya kikundi\", \"Upendo: mwanafunzi anapopewa nafasi ya kushiriki katika shughuli za ujifunzaji darasani na katika kikundi\", \"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapojitolea kuchukua nafasi mbalimbali katika shughuli za kikundi\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake katika shughuli za kikundi\"]','[\"Elimu ya kifedha: mwanafunzi anapotoa mawaidha kuhusu matumizi ya kodi\"]','[\"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha dhana ya mazungumzo katika somo la Kiswahili na dhana hiyo katika somo la English\", \"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha suala la matumizi ya kodi na yale amejifunza kuhusu suala hilo katika somo la Pre-Technical Studies na Religious Education\"]',101,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35676,8904,'14.2.1','Kusoma kwa Ufahamu - Kifungu cha Mjadala',2,'[\"kudondoa habari mahususi katika kifungu cha mjadala\", \"kueleza maana za maneno kama yalivyotumiwa katika kifungu cha mjadala\", \"kufanya utabiri na ufasiri kutokana na kifungu cha mjadala\", \"kuchangamkia kusoma kwa ufahamu ili kukuza uelewa wa habari mahususi\"]','[\"kudondoa habari mahususi katika kifungu cha mjadala\", \"kueleza habari za kifungu cha mjadala kwa ufupi\", \"kufanya utabiri na ufasiri kutokana na kifungu cha mjadala\", \"kusoma mtandaoni kifungu cha mjadala na kufupisha habari mahususi\", \"kumsomea mzazi, mlezi au mwenzake kifungu cha mjadala aliyokisoma na kujadili habari zilizomo\"]','[\"Ni mambo gani unayofanya kusoma kwa ufahamu?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki na kuchangia ipasavyo katika kusoma kwa ufahamu\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia vifaa vya kidijitali kusoma kwa ufahamu\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapoweza kusoma kwa ufahamu\", \"Uwazaji kina na utatuzi wa matatizo: mwanafunzi anapodondoa habari mahususi kutokana na kifungu cha mjadala\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapothamini maoni ya wenzake katika kazi ya kikundi\", \"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapojitolea kuchukua nafasi mbalimbali katika shughuli za kikundi\"]','[\"Elimu ya kifedha: mwanafunzi anaposoma matini kuhusu matumizi ya kodi\"]','[\"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha dhana ya kusoma kwa ufahamu katika somo la Kiswahili na dhana hiyo katika somo la English\", \"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha suala la matumizi ya kodi na yale amejifunza kuhusu suala hilo katika somo la Pre-Technical Studies na Religious Education\"]',201,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35677,8904,'14.3.1','Insha za Kiuamilifu - Shajara',2,'[\"kujadili umuhimu wa shajara\", \"kujadili vipengele vya shajara\", \"kueleza aina za shajara\", \"kuandika aina za shajara akizingatia vipengele vya uandishi wa shajara\", \"kufurahia kuandika aina za shajara\"]','[\"kutafiti maktabani au mtandaoni salama na kujadili shajara\", \"kujadili na wenzake aina za shajara\", \"kueleza aina za shajara\", \"kuandika aina za shajara akizingatia vipengele vya uandishi wa shajara\", \"kuwasomea wenzake shajara aliyoandika ili waitolee maoni\"]','[\"Je, ni mambo gani unazingatia unapoandika shajara?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake katika kujadili aina za shajara\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia vifaa vya kidijitali kuandika shajara\", \"Ubunifu: mwanafunzi anapoweza kubuni aina za shajara\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapoweza kuwasomea wenzake shajara aliyoandika\", \"Hamu ya ujifunzaji: mwanafunzi anapotafiti na kujifunza kuhusu aina za shajara\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapothamini maoni ya wenzake katika kazi ya kikundi\", \"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapojitolea kuchukua nafasi mbalimbali katika shughuli za kikundi\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake katika shughuli za kikundi\"]','[\"Elimu ya kifedha: mwanafunzi anapoandika shajara kuhusu matumizi ya kodi\"]','[\"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha uandishi wa shajara katika somo la Kiswahili na dhana hiyo katika somo la English\", \"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha suala la matumizi ya kodi na yale amejifunza kuhusu suala hilo katika somo la Pre-Technical Studies na Religious Education\"]',301,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35678,8904,'14.4.1','Udogo na Ukubwa wa Nomino',2,'[\"kutambua hali ya udogo na ukubwa katika nomino\", \"kutumia nomino katika hali ya udogo na ukubwa ipasavyo katika matini\", \"kuchangamkia kutumia kwa ufasaha nomino katika hali ya udogo na ukubwa ili kufanikisha mawasiliano\"]','[\"kuchopoa nomino katika hali ya udogo na ukubwa kwenye chati, kadi maneno, kapu maneno au tarakilishi\", \"kutambua viambishi vya udogo na ukubwa katika maneno\", \"kuandika majina ya vifaa vya darasani katika udogo na ukubwa\", \"kuambatanisha nomino za hali ya wastani na za hali ya udogo na ukubwa kwa usahihi kwenye chati za maneno\", \"kujaza nafasi katika sentensi kwa kutumia nomino katika hali ya udogo au ukubwa\", \"kutunga sentensi akitumia nomino katika hali ya udogo na ukubwa kwa kuzingatia masuala mtambuko mbalimbali likiwemo suala la matumizi ya kodi\", \"kumtajia mzazi au mlezi wake majina ya vifaa vya nyumbani katika udogo na ukubwa katika mazingira ya nyumbani\"]','[\"Ni maneno gani unayoyajua yaliyoko katika hali ya ukubwa?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki kazi za kikundi\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia vifaa vya kiteknolojia kutambua nomino katika hali ya udogo na ukubwa\", \"Ubunifu: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi sahihi kuhusu suala lengwa akitumia nomino katika hali ya udogo na ukubwa\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapofaulu kutambua nomino katika hali ya udogo na ukubwa na kuzitungia sentensi\", \"Hamu ya ujifunzaji: mwanafunzi anapomtajia mzazi au mlezi wake nomino katika hali ya udogo na udogo katika mazingira ya nyumbani\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapoheshimu maoni ya wenzake katika kazi ya kikundi\", \"Upendo: mwanafunzi anapopewa nafasi ya kushiriki katika shughuli za ujifunzaji darasani na katika kikundi\", \"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapojitolea kuchukua nafasi mbalimbali katika shughuli za kikundi\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki katika shughuli za kikundi\"]','[\"Elimu ya kifedha: mwanafunzi anapoandika sentensi kuhusu matumizi ya kodi kwa kutumia nomino katika hali ya udogo na ukubwa\"]','[\"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha dhana ya nomino katika somo la Kiswahili na dhana hiyo katika somo la English\", \"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha suala la matumizi ya kodi na yale amejifunza kuhusu suala hilo katika somo la Pre-Technical Studies na Religious Education\"]',401,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35679,8905,'15.1.1','Kusikiliza kwa Kutathmini',2,'[\"kueleza maana ya kusikiliza kwa kutathmini\", \"kujadili vipengele vya kuzingatia katika kutathmini mazungumzo\", \"kusikiliza mazungumzo na kuyatathmini kwa kuzingatia vipengele vifaavyo\", \"kuchangamkia kutathmini mazungumzo ili kuimarisha mawasiliano\"]','[\"kutafiti na kueleza maana ya kusikiliza kwa kutathmini\", \"kujadili na wenzake vipengele vya kuzingatia katika kutathmini mazungumzo kutoka kwenye mazungumzo mafupi\", \"kusikiliza mazungumzo kuhusu suala lengwa kutoka kwa mwalimu, mgeni mwalikwa au kwenye vifaa vya kidijitali na kuyatathmini kwa kuzingatia vipengele mbalimbali\", \"kushiriki na mzazi au mlezi wake katika mazungumzo kuhusu suala lengwa na kutoa maoni kuhusu suala linalozungumziwa\"]','[\"Kusikiliza kwa kutathmini mazungumzo kuna umuhimu gani?\", \"Unazingatia nini katika kutathmini ufaafu wa mazungumzo?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki na kuchangia katika kujadili kuhusu vipengele vya kuzingatia katika kusikiliza kwa kutathmini\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia vifaa vya kidijitali kusikilizia mazungumzo kuhusu suala lengwa na kutathmini\", \"Uwazaji kina na utatuzi wa matatizo: mwanafunzi anapotathmini yaliyozungumziwa na kutoa uamuzi kuhusu vipengele ambavyo vimetumiwa\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapofanikiwa kutoa mtazamo wake kuhusu suala linalozungumziwa katika mazungumzo aliyoyasikiliza\", \"Hamu ya ujifunzaji: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki mazungumzo kuhusu suala lengwa na mzazi au mlezi wake na kujifunza zaidi vipengele vya kusikiliza kwa kutathmini\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapoyathamini maoni ya wenzake katika shughuli za kikundi\", \"Upendo: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake katika kikundi\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki na kuchangia katika shughuli za kikundi\"]','[\"Maadili ya kitaifa: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana wenzake katika mazungumzo kuhusu suala lengwa\"]','[\"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha dhana ya aina za uzungumzaji katika somo la Kiswahili na dhana hiyo katika somo la English\", \"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha suala la maadili ya kitaifa na yale amejifunza kuhusu suala hilo katika somo la Social Studies na Religious Education\"]',101,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35680,8905,'15.2.1','Ufupisho',2,'[\"kujadili vipengele vya kuzingatia katika ufupisho wa habari katika matini\", \"kuandika ufupisho wa habari kwa kuzingatia vipengele vifaavyo\", \"kufurahia kufupisha habari kwa usahihi katika miktadha mbalimbali\"]','[\"kujadili na wenzake vipengele vya ufupisho wa habari katika matini (kuzingatia maelekezo ya ufupisho, kueleza habari upya kwa maneno yake mwenyewe, kudondosha mifano na maelezo ya ziada, mpangilio wenye muwala)\", \"kuandika ufupisho wa habari kwa kuzingatia vipengele vifaavyo na kuwasomea wenzake ili watoe maoni yao\", \"kusoma matini mbalimbali zikiwemo za mtandaoni na kufupisha habari kwa usahihi\", \"kumsomea mzazi, mlezi au mwenzake habari aliyoifupisha kutoka katika matini aliyoisoma ili aitolee maoni\"]','[\"Unazingatia nini ili kuandika ufupisho ufaao?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anapojadiliana na wenzake kuhusu vipengele vya kuzingatia katika ufupisho wa habari\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia vifaa vya kidijitali katika kusoma makala\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapoeleza kwa kifupi makala aliyosoma\", \"Hamu ya ujifunzaji: mwanafunzi anaposoma makala kutoka mtandaoni na kuyafupisha ipasavyo\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapothamini maoni ya wenzake katika kazi ya kikundi\", \"Upendo: mwanafunzi anapopewa nafasi ya kushiriki katika shughuli za ujifunzaji\", \"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapojitolea kuchukua nafasi mbalimbali katika shughuli za kikundi\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki katika shughuli za kikundi\"]','[\"Maadili ya kitaifa: mwanafunzi anaposoma na kufupisha habari katika matini kuhusu suala lengwa\"]','[\"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha dhana ya ufupisho katika somo la Kiswahili na dhana hiyo katika somo la English\", \"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha suala la maadili ya kitaifa na yale amejifunza kuhusu suala hilo katika somo la Social Studies na Religious Education\"]',201,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO `template_substrands` VALUES (35681,8905,'15.3.1','Kujibu Baruapepe',2,'[\"kujadili vipengele vya kuzingatia katika kujibu baruapepe\", \"kujibu baruapepe kwa kuzingatia vipengele vifaavyo\", \"kujenga mazoea ya kujibu baruapepe ipasavyo\"]','[\"kujadili na wenzake vipengele vya kuzingatia katika kujibu baruapepe\", \"kutambua na kutumia lugha inayofaa kwa uandishi wa barua ya kujibu baruapepe\", \"kujadili na wenzake vidokezo vya kutumia katika kujibu baruapepe\", \"kuandika barua baruapepe kuhusu suala lengwa kwenye tarakilishi na kuwasambazia wenzake kupitia mtandao\", \"kumweleza mzazi, mlezi au mwenzake namna ya kujibu baruapepe ili waitolee maoni\"]','[\"Je, ni mambo gani ya kuzingatia unapoandika baruapepe?\", \"Je, ni mambo gani ya kuzingatia katika kujibu baruapepe?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anapojadiliana na wenzake kuhusu vipengele vya kuzingatia katika kujibu baruapepe\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia vifaa vya kidijitali kuandika baruapepe na kuisambazia wenzake\", \"Ubunifu: mwanafunzi anapoandika baruapepe ipasavyo\", \"Hamu ya ujifunzaji: mwanafunzi anapomwelezea mzazi au mlezi wake namna ya kujibu baruapepe\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapothamini maoni ya wenzake katika kazi ya kikundi\", \"Upendo: mwanafunzi anapopewa nafasi ya kushiriki katika shughuli za ujifunzaji darasani na katika kikundi\", \"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapojitolea kuchukua nafasi mbalimbali katika shughuli za kikundi\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake katika shughuli za kikundi\"]','[\"Maadili ya kitaifa: mwanafunzi anapoandika baruapepe kuhusu suala lengwa\"]','[\"Mwanafunji anaweza kuhusisha dhana ya uandishi wa kidijitali katika somo la Kiswahili na dhana hiyo katika somo la English\", \"Mwanafunji anaweza kuhusisha suala la maadili ya kitaifa na yale amejifunza kuhusu suala hilo katika somo la Social Studies na Religious Education\"]',301,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35682,8905,'15.4.1','Usemi Halisi na Usemi wa Taarifa',2,'[\"kujadili kanuni za kubadilisha usemi halisi kuwa usemi wa taarifa\", \"kutumia usemi halisi na usemi wa taarifa ipasavyo katika matini\", \"kuchangamkia matumizi ya usemi halisi na usemi wa taarifa katika mawasiliano ya kila siku\"]','[\"kujadiliana na wenzake kanuni za kubadilisha usemi halisi kuwa usemi wa taarifa\", \"kugeuza sentensi zilizo katika usemi halisi ziwe katika usemi wa taarifa\", \"kugeuza sentensi zilizo katika usemi wa taarifa ziwe katika usemi halisi\", \"kushiriki katika mchezo wa kuchopoa kadi katika vikundi. Kikundi kimoja kichopoe kadi ya sentensi sahili katika usemi halisi na kikundi kingine kichopoe sentensi hiyo katika usemi wa taarifa\", \"kutunga sentensi sahili katika usemi halisi na usemi wa taarifa daftarini mwake kwa kuzingatia masuala mtambuko mbalimbali likiwemo suala maadili ya kitaifa\", \"kumsomea mzazi, mlezi au mwenzake sentensi sahili alizotunga za usemi halisi na usemi wa taarifa ili kuzitolea maoni\"]','[\"Usemi halisi unatofautianaje na usemi wa taarifa?\", \"Unazingatia nini unapoandika usemi halisi?\", \"Unazingatia nini unapoandika usemi wa taarifa?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhiriki katika shughuli za kikundi na kujadili kuhusu usemi halisi na usemi wa taarifa\", \"Ubunifu: mwanafunzi anapotunga sentensi sahihi za usemi halisi na usemi wa taarifa\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapomsomea mwenzake sentensi sahihi za usemi halisi na usemi wa taarifa\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapothamini maoni ya wenzake katika kazi ya kikundi\", \"Upendo: mwanafunzi anapopewa nafasi ya kushiriki katika shughuli za ujifunzaji darasani na katika kikundi\", \"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapojitolea kuchukua nafasi mbalimbali katika shughuli za kikundi\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake katika shughuli za kikundi\"]','[\"Maadili ya kitaifa: mwanafunzi anapotumia usemi halisi na usemi wa taarifa kuhusu suala lengwa\", \"Masuala mtambuko mbalimbali kulingana na sentensi zilizotungwa\"]','[\"Mwanafunji anaweza kuhusisha dhana ya usemi halisi na usemi wa taarifa katika somo la Kiswahili na dhana hiyo katika somo la English\", \"Mwanafunji anaweza kuhusisha suala la maadili ya kitaifa na yale amejifunza kuhusu suala hilo katika somo la Social Studies na Religious Education\"]',401,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35683,8906,'1.1','INTEGERS',5,'[\"perform basic operations on Integers in different situations\", \"work out combined Operations on Integers in different situations\", \"apply Integers to real life situations\", \"use IT or other resources to learn more on integers\", \"appreciate use of integers in real life situations\"]','[\"discuss and work out basic operations on integers using number cards and charts. Play games involving numbers and operations. Pick integers and perform all basic operations.\", \"work out combined operations of integers in the correct order\", \"carry out activities such as reading temperature changes in a thermometer and discuss how to record it. Consider temperatures below zero points. They should consider cases of use of integers in real life.\", \"use IT and other resources such as print to carry out operations on integers.\", \"play creative games that involve integers.\"]','[\"How do we carry out operations of integers in real life situations?\", \"How do we apply integers in daily activities?\"]','[\"Critical thinking and problem solving- interpretation and inference: as learners work out combined operations of integers in the correct order\", \"Learning to learn- organizing own learning; as learners carry out activities such as reading temperature changes in a thermometer and discuss how to record it.\", \"Digital literacy- interacting with technologies; as learners use IT devices to determine temperature.\"]','[\"Respect; as learners work in pairs/groups to carry out activities such as reading temperature changes in a thermometer and discuss how to record it.\", \"Unity; as learners work towards achieving set goals of reading thermometer.\"]','[\"Environmental education; as learners read temperature changes in a thermometer that tell about the climate\"]','[]',1,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35684,8906,'1.2','CUBES AND CUBE ROOTS',5,'[\"Work out cubes of numbers by multiplication in real life situations\", \"Determine cubes of numbers from mathematical tables in different situations\", \"Determine cube roots of numbers by factor method in different situations\", \"Determine cube roots of numbers from mathematical tables in different situations\", \"Apply cubes and cube roots in real life situations\", \"Work out cubes and cube roots using IT devices\"]','[\"use stacks of cubes to demonstrate the concept of cube and cube roots.\", \"demonstrate stacking of cubes.\", \"discuss the volume of a cube and determine both the cube and cube root and relate the two.\", \"read the cube of numbers from mathematical tables and relate to cube roots\", \"use IT devices to determine cube and cube roots of numbers.\"]','[\"How do we work out the cubes of numbers?\", \"How do we work out the cube roots of numbers?\", \"Where do we apply cubes and cube roots in real life situations?\"]','[\"Communication and collaboration- speaking and listening; as learners work in groups to use stacks of cubes to demonstrate the concept of cube and cube roots.\", \"Imagination and creativity- open mindedness and creativity; as learners determine both the cube and cube root and relate the two.\"]','[\"Respect; as learners appreciate each other\'s contribution in pairs/groups discussion.\"]','[]','[]',2,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35685,8906,'1.3','INDICES AND LOGARITHMS',6,'[\"Express numbers in index form in different situations\", \"Generate the laws of Indices in different situations\", \"Apply the laws of indices in different situations\", \"Relate Powers of 10 to common logarithms in different situations\", \"Use IT to learn more on indices and common logarithms\", \"Appreciate use of indices and logarithms in real life situations\"]','[\"discuss indices and identify the base.\", \"show the laws of indices using multiplication and division.\", \"use the laws of indices to work out indices\", \"discuss and relate powers of 10 to common logarithms\", \"use IT to work out common logarithms or use mathematical tables\"]','[\"How do we express numbers in powers?\"]','[\"Critical thinking and problem solving; as learners show the laws of indices using multiplication and division.\", \"Self-efficacy; as learners discuss and relate powers of 10 to common logarithms\"]','[\"Responsibility; as learners take their roles in turns to lead the groups in discussions on indices.\", \"Unity; as learners measure capacity in groups.\"]','[\"Learners relate self-awareness to their own ides as they discuss concept of Indices.\"]','[]',3,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35686,8906,'1.4','COMPOUND PROPORTIONS AND RATES OF WORK',12,'[\"divide quantities into proportional parts in real life situations\", \"relate different ratios in real life situations\", \"work out compound proportions using ratio method in different situations\", \"calculate rates of work in real life situations\", \"use IT devices to learn more on Compound proportions and rates of work\", \"appreciate use of Compound proportions and rates of work in real life situations\"]','[\"discuss and divide quantities into proportional parts and express as a fraction\", \"compare and write different ratios\", \"determine compound proportions using ratios\", \"work out rates of work.\", \"play games on rates of work using IT devices.\"]','[\"What are proportions?\", \"Why do we work fast?\"]','[\"Citizenship- active community life skills; as learners work in pairs/groups to discuss and divide quantities into proportional parts and express as a fraction.\", \"Critical thinking and problem solving- interpretation and inference; as learners work out rates of work.\"]','[\"Responsibility; as learners commit to working out answers of given tasks on rates.\", \"Respect for self and others; as learners in pairs/groups and work out rates of work.\"]','[\"Self-esteem; as learners device personal strategies to estimate products in multiplication.\"]','[]',4,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35687,8907,'2.1','MATRICES',8,'[\"identify a matrix in different situations\", \"determine the order of a matrix in different situations\", \"determine the position of items in a matrix in different situations\", \"determine compatibility of matrices in addition and subtraction\", \"carry out addition and subtraction of matrices in real life situations\", \"reflect on the use of matrices in real life situations\"]','[\"discuss the use of tables such as football league tables, travel schedules, shopping lists and any other. Count the number of rows and columns in the table, which is a matrix.\", \"arrange items in rows and columns and discuss how to represent a matrix.\", \"organize objects in rows and columns and give the order of the matrix in terms of row and columns (row x column).\", \"discuss and identify the position of each item or element in terms of row and column.\", \"discuss and identify matrices that have equal number of rows and equal number of columns (same order) for compatibility in addition and subtraction.\", \"discuss and note what is represented by the rows and what is represented by the columns from two or more matrices to carry out addition or subtraction.\"]','[\"How do we use matrices in real life situations?\"]','[\"Communication and collaboration - as learners discuss use of tables to represent matrices.\", \"Learning to learn - as learners arrange items or elements in rows and columns to form matrices.\"]','[\"Integrity - as learners organize objects in rows and columns and give the order of the matrix\"]','[\"Social and economic issues - as learners discuss the use of tables such as football league tables and shopping lists.\", \"Citizenship - as learners discuss how to use travel schedules to different places.\"]','[]',1,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35688,8907,'2.2','EQUATIONS OF A STRAIGHT LINE',15,'[\"identify the gradient in real life situations\", \"determine the gradient of a line from two known points\", \"determine the equation of a straight line given two points\", \"determine the equation of a straight line from a known point and a gradient\", \"express the equation of a straight line in the form of 𝑦 = 𝑚𝑥+ 𝑐\", \"interpret the equation 𝑦 = 𝑚𝑥+ 𝑐 in different situations\", \"determine the x and y intercepts of a straight line\", \"recognize the use of equations of straight lines in real life\"]','[\"discuss steepness in relation to gradient from the immediate environment.\", \"incline a ladder at different positions on the wall to demonstrate change in steepness of gradient. Discuss and compare the positions that the ladder is steeper.\", \"observe and climb up and down places such as the stairs or hills and relate to gradients.\", \"work out the equation of a straight line given two points or given a point and a gradient.\", \"discuss and rewrite the equation of a straight line as 𝑦 = 𝑚𝑥+ 𝑐. Explain the variables and constants in the equation.\", \"work out the value of x when y is zero and the value of y when is zero.\", \"use IT or other resources to show different hills and mountains and discuss steepness.\"]','[\"How do we use gradient or steepness in our daily activities?\", \"How do we interpret graphs of straight lines?\"]','[\"Digital literacy - as learners IT or others resources to explore steepness or gradient of places.\", \"Learning to learn - as learners place the ladder at different points on the ground as they discuss and compare steepness.\"]','[\"Integrity - as learners observe gradient/steepness in staircases in buildings, bridges or ramps.\"]','[\"Safety - as learners climb up and down places such as the stairs or hills and relate to gradients.\", \"Education for Sustainable Development (ESD) - as learners participate and choose careers in games and sporting activities.\"]','[]',2,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35689,8907,'2.3','LINEAR INEQUALITIES',6,'[\"solve linear inequalities in one unknown\", \"represent linear inequalities in one unknown graphically\", \"represent linear inequality in two unknowns graphically\", \"apply linear inequalities to real life situations\", \"reflect on the use of linear inequalities in real life\"]','[\"discuss why sometimes resources are shared unequally.\", \"discuss simple inequality statements, form and work out the inequalities in one unknown.\", \"discuss and generate a table of values and draw linear inequalities in one unknown. Indicate and discuss the region that satisfies the inequalities.\", \"discuss and generate a table of values and draw linear inequalities in two unknowns. Indicate and discuss the region that satisfies the inequalities.\", \"discuss and work out linear inequalities that involve real life cases\", \"use IT or other graphing tools to present linear inequalities\"]','[\"How do we represent linear inequalities in graphs?\", \"How do we use linear inequalities in real life situations?\"]','[\"Digital literacy - as learners use IT resources to present linear inequalities.\", \"Communication and collaboration - as learners discuss and generate table of values and draw linear inequalities.\"]','[\"Social justice - as learners apply concepts of inequalities and equity in sharing available resources real in life situations.\"]','[\"Citizenship - as learners discuss and indicate the regions that satisfy inequalities.\"]','[]',3,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35690,8908,'3.1','AREA',8,'[\"calculate the area of a pentagon and a hexagon in different situations\", \"work out the surface area of triangular and rectangular based prisms\", \"work out the surface area of triangular, rectangular and square based pyramids\", \"calculate the area of a sector and segment of a circle\", \"work out the surface area of a cone in real life situations\", \"calculate the surface area of a sphere in real life situations\", \"recognize the use of area in real life situations\"]','[\"discuss the properties of regular polygons and use cut outs to work out the area of pentagons and hexagons.\", \"collect from the environment objects that are spheres, cones/funnels, pyramids, prisms and frustums.\", \"discuss and sketch the nets of the solids.\", \"use models of prisms to work out the surface area of prisms.\", \"open up the net and draw the faces of a pyramid. Use the relevant formulas of area of plane figures to work out the surface area of the pyramid.\", \"draw a circle with a sector, a chord and a segment and discuss the relationship and make cut outs of a sector and a segment. Determine the area of a sector and a segment.\", \"open the cone to form a net and determine the curved surface area of a cone. Work out the surface area of a closed and an open cone.\", \"use relevant formulas to work out the surface area of different sizes of spherical balls.\", \"use IT or other resources to sketch different models and nets.\"]','[\"How do we determine the area of different surfaces?\"]','[\"Communication and collaboration - as learners work in groups to discuss the properties of regular polygons and use cutouts to work out the area of pentagon and hexagon.\", \"Creativity and imagination - as learners open nets of different models and work out surface area.\"]','[\"Responsibility - as learners take care and work out surface area using models and open nets of different objects.\"]','[\"Patriotism - as learners collect objects from the environment, use and dispose of them safely.\"]','[]',1,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35691,8908,'3.2','VOLUME OF SOLIDS',8,'[\"work out the volume of a triangular and rectangular based prisms\", \"calculate the volume of a triangular, rectangular and squares based pyramids\", \"work out the volume of a cone in real life situations\", \"determine the volume of a frustum in real life situations\", \"calculate the volume of a sphere in real life situations\", \"promote use of volume and capacity of different containers in real life situations\"]','[\"collect different containers and objects. This may include prisms, pyramids, cones, funnels and balls.\", \"identify and discuss the model of a prism. Using the relevant formulas, determine the volume of a prism.\", \"use relevant formulae to work out the volume of pyramids and cones.\", \"identify and work out the volume of models of a pyramid. Cut the pyramid into two parts to get a frustum and a small pyramid and determine the volume of the frustum using relevant formula.\", \"Play any games involving different sizes of balls and work out volume of a sphere.\", \"use IT or other resources to determine the volumes of solids.\"]','[\"How do we determine the volume of different solids?\", \"How do we use the volume of solids in real life situations?\"]','[\"Critical thinking and problem solving - as learners identify and work out the volume of a frustum from a pyramid\", \"Creativity and Imagination - as learners identify, discuss and work out volume of solids.\"]','[\"Responsibility - as learners take care of the models of pyramids, cones, and spheres.\", \"Patriotism - as learners collect objects from the environment to determine and discuss models/objects for different volumes of solids.\"]','[\"Environmental Education - as learners take care of the environment while collecting the containers and objects.\", \"Safety - as learners collect containers and objects cautiously.\"]','[]',2,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35692,8908,'3.3','MASS, VOLUME, WEIGHT AND DENSITY',8,'[\"convert units of mass from one form to another in different situations\", \"relate mass and weight in real life situations\", \"determine mass, volume and density in different situations\", \"apply density to real life situations\", \"recognize the use of density in daily life\"]','[\"discuss different instruments and tools used in weighing materials or objects and relate to consumer awareness and protection.\", \"Collect and weigh different materials or objects and change one unit of mass to another.\", \"discuss the relationship between mass and weight.\", \"carry out activities relating mass and volume to density using containers or different substances.\", \"discuss and find the density of different materials or objects.\", \"work out mass, volume and density using IT or other resources.\"]','[\"How do you weigh materials and objects?\"]','[\"Communication and collaboration - as learners discuss the relationship between mass and weight.\", \"Creativity and imagination - as learners determine the density of different materials or objects.\", \"Digital literacy - as learners use IT devices to determine the mass, volume and density of different objects.\"]','[\"Integrity - as learners give correct masses and weights of different material and objects.\", \"Responsibility - as learners work and take care of weighing machines and other resources.\"]','[\"Education for Sustainable Development (ESD) - Careers in business such as shop keeping.\", \"Self-awareness - as learners weigh themselves for health purposes.\"]','[]',3,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35693,8908,'3.4','TIME, DISTANCE AND SPEED',10,'[\"work out speed in km/h and m/s in real life situations\", \"work out average speed in real life situations\", \"determine velocity in real life situations\", \"work out acceleration in real life situations\", \"identify the longitudes on the globe\", \"relate longitudes to time on the globe\", \"determine local time of places on the earth along different longitudes\", \"appreciate use of time and distance in real life situations\"]','[\"engage in activities that will involve measuring distances and time, for example running track events to determine speed.\", \"discuss and relate distance and time.\", \"discuss the difference between velocity and speed.\", \"Discuss and determine acceleration from track events in school or community.\", \"discuss and use maps and models of a globe to work out and relate time of different places on the earth.\", \"use IT devices to watch videos on the globe, longitudes and time zones in different parts of the earth.\", \"use other resources such as maps to locate different places (cities) on the earth and discuss time differences.\"]','[\"How do we observe speed in daily activities?\", \"Why does time vary in different places of the world?\"]','[\"Self-efficacy - as learners participate in track events to measure speed.\", \"Digital literacy -as learners use IT devices to determine time in different zones in the world.\", \"Citizenship- global citizenship as learners determine local time in different parts of the world.\"]','[\"Integrity- as learners correctly record individual running time during track events and other games.\", \"Respect - as learners adhere to their lanes on track events and other games.\"]','[\"Safety - as learners observe safety measures and time during games and sports.\", \"Education for Sustainable Development (ESD) - as learners participate and choose careers in games and sporting activities.\", \"Self-awareness - as learners participate and time themselves in games.\"]','[]',4,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35694,8908,'3.5','MONEY',7,'[\"identify currencies that are used in different countries\", \"convert currency from one form to another in real life situations\", \"work out import and export duties charged on goods and services\", \"work out excise duty charged on goods and services\", \"determine value added tax charged on goods and services\", \"appreciate use of money in day to day activities\"]','[\"use IT or other resources to obtain and compile a collage of currencies from different countries. For example, currencies of East African Countries, US dollars, Euro, Yen and Sterling pound.\", \"work out currency exchange from Kenya Shillings to any other currency and vice versa.\", \"discuss and determine the export and import duty charges on different goods.\", \"discuss and identify goods that attract excise duty. Determine excise duty.\", \"use receipts from shopping to discuss and work out VAT on goods and services.\", \"identify currency exchange rates from different sources including daily papers, IT devices, financial institutions and relate this to consumer awareness and protection.\"]','[\"Why do we change currencies from one form to another?\", \"What are the types of taxes the government levy on its citizens?\"]','[\"Global Citizenship - as learners of different currencies of the world.\", \"Digital Literacy - as learners use digital devices to learn on exchange rates for foreign currency.\"]','[\"Integrity - as learners accurately work out currency, import and exchange rates.\", \"Social Cohesion - as learners work and appreciate exchange rates for other countries.\"]','[\"Financial Literacy - as learners learn the currencies used in different countries\", \"Education for Sustainable Development (ESD) - as learners choose careers in business, imports and exports.\"]','[]',5,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35695,8908,'3.6','APPROXIMATIONS AND ERRORS',5,'[\"approximate quantities in measurements in different situations\", \"determine errors using estimations and actual measurements of quantities\", \"determine percentage errors using actual measurements of quantities\", \"appreciate approximations and errors in real life situations\"]','[\"carryout activities of measurements of different quantities such as length, area, volume, capacity and mass using arbitrary units.\", \"Estimate and measure different quantities using appropriate instruments. compare the estimates and the actual measurements and determine the error.\", \"work out the percentage error from the estimated and the actual measurements\", \"work out errors using IT devices or other resources and relate this to consumer awareness.\"]','[\"How do we estimate measurements of different quantities?\"]','[\"Creativity and imagination - as learners carry out measurements of different quantities and discuss error.\", \"Digital literacy - as learners use IT devices as they compute errors.\"]','[\"Integrity - as learners measure different quantities and minimize errors.\", \"Responsibility - as learners take care of tools for measuring different quantities.\"]','[\"Safety - as learners handle measuring tools with care.\"]','[]',6,'2025-12-07 19:11:30',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35696,8909,'4.1','COORDINATES AND GRAPHS',6,'[\"plot out points on a Cartesian plane\", \"draw a straight line graph given an equation\", \"draw parallel lines on the Cartesian plane\", \"relate the gradients of parallel lines\", \"draw perpendicular lines on the Cartesian plane\", \"relate the gradients of perpendicular lines\", \"apply graphs of straight line in real life situation\"]','[\"work in groups and locate the point of intersection of the x coordinate and the y- coordinates on a Cartesian plane.\", \"generate a table of values from equation a of a straight line, plot and join the points to form a straight line.\", \"Generate table of values for each of the given equations, plot and join them to form straight lines on the Cartesian plane\", \"work out the gradients of each of the lines and compare them to establish their relationship of parallelism.\", \"Generate table of values for each of the given equations of perpendicular lines, plot and join them to form straight lines on the Cartesian plane\", \"work out the gradients of each of the lines and compare them to establish the relationship of perpendicular lines.\"]','[\"How do we draw graphs of straight lines?\", \"How do we interpret graphs of straight lines?\"]','[\"Communication and collaboration\", \"Critical thinking and problem solving - as learners generate a table of values.\"]','[\"Responsibility - as l