: learners avoid early marriage by not engaging in irresponsible sexual behavior\"]','[\"Social Studies: learners outline virtues that both partners should uphold before marriage\", \"English: learners debate on the motion: \'Courtship is important before marriage.\'\"]',1,'2025-12-07 19:11:31',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35729,8920,'5.2','Responsible Parenthood',6,'[\"describe biblical teachings on responsible parenthood\", \"discuss causes of irresponsible parenting today\", \"appraise the role of parents/guardians in shaping the character of their children\", \"appreciate good parenting as guided by the Bible\"]','[\"use relevant textbooks or internet sources to search for the meaning of responsible parenthood and share findings with the class\", \"in groups read, Exodus 20:12, Deuteronomy 11:18-21, Psalms 103:13, Proverbs 15:20, Proverbs 22:6, and Colossians 3:21, discuss and write lessons learned on a chart or use PowerPoint slides for presentation in class\", \"discuss the causes of irresponsible parenting\", \"brainstorm on ways of avoiding unplanned families\", \"conduct a buzz session on moral values needed to avoid unplanned families\", \"come up with a play/drama on good parenting\", \"in groups debate on the role of parents/guardians in instilling good moral values in children and note key points\"]','[\"How is responsible parenthood achieved?\"]','[\"Communication and Collaboration: the skill of teamwork is enhanced as learners collegially work in group discussions/brainstorm/buzz and express/defend their views confidently\", \"Digital Literacy: the skill of identifying and using digital platforms for learning is portrayed as learners search the internet to get information on different assignments\", \"Creativity and imagination: the skill of creativity is exhibited as learners come up with scenarios on good parenting through dramatization and role-play\"]','[\"Integrity: is portrayed as learners follow laid down procedures when executing tasks/have self-discipline\", \"Responsibility: is exhibited as learners engage in assigned roles and duties/they are also accountable for their own actions\", \"Social Justice: is enhanced as learners identify values/virtues needed for responsible parenting and harmonious family relationships\"]','[\"Learner support programmes-Decision-making-for transition in life: Guidance and counseling in the school will support learners at different levels of growth and development\", \"Human sexuality: learners will acquire life skills that enable them to overcome growth and developmental changes\", \"Assertiveness: learners exhibit self-esteem by making the right decisions and avoid negative peer influence by not engaging in vices/situations that can lead to unplanned families\", \"Information Technology: learners will use digital devices and applications ethically/exercise self-discipline as they search and download information from the internet\"]','[\"Pre-technical Studies: learners use digital devices to search the internet for information they need to complete assigned tasks\", \"Creative Arts and Sports: learners come up with a play/drama on good parenting\", \"English: learners read and discuss in groups the Bible texts provided they also present findings confidently in class\"]',2,'2025-12-07 19:11:31',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35730,8920,'5.3','Leisure',6,'[\"identify different forms of leisure today\", \"analyse how youths misuse leisure today\", \"identify Christian moral values needed to avoid alcohol, drugs and substances use\", \"evaluate the effects of alcohol, drug and substance use on an individual\", \"utilize Christian moral values to avoid alcohol, drug and substance use\"]','[\"in pairs brainstorm on the different forms of leisure\", \"share experiences on how they spend their free time\", \"in groups discuss why and how youths misuse leisure today\", \"discuss the effects of alcohol, drug and substance use on an individual and make notes/PowerPoint slides for class presentation\", \"in pairs write and recite poems on, \'Alcohol drug, and substance use is detrimental to health\'\", \"read and write (1 Timothy 5:13, Ecclesiastes 10:18, Proverbs 19:15) on flashcards and outline lessons learnt\", \"identify values and life skills needed to avoid alcohol, drug and substance use\", \"debate on the motion, \'An idle mind is the devil\'s workshop\'\", \"write and keep a reflection journal on how they spend their free time\"]','[\"Why do youths misuse leisure today?\", \"How can you avoid idleness?\"]','[\"Self-Efficacy: the skill of self-awareness and planning is portrayed as learners set goals on how to use leisure time appropriately\", \"Critical thinking and problem-solving: research skills, interpretation and inference are exhibited as learners explore effects of alcohol, drug and substance use on an individual\", \"Citizenship: social and civic skills are demonstrated as the learner is aware of own responsibilities in the society, thus obeys laws and regulations by not engaging in alcohol, drug and substance use\"]','[\"Respect: is demonstrated as learners desire to respect self by not engaging in alcohol, drug and substance use\", \"Responsibility: the learners set goals on how to use leisure time responsibly\", \"Patriotism: the learner is conscious of their own social and moral duties thus use leisure time responsibly\"]','[\"Decision-making: learners commit themselves to using leisure time well\", \"Assertiveness: learners make a decision to use leisure time responsibly and avoid idleness\", \"Health Promotion Issues-Drug and substance use: learners write a poem on the effects of alcohol, drug and substance use on an individual\", \"Counseling services-Positive behavior change: learners are guided on proper use of leisure and those who are affected by drug and substance use are given support by the school/parents/guardians to positively change their behavior\"]','[\"English: learners in pairs brainstorm on the different forms of leisure and make a presentation using PowerPoint slides/charts\", \"Social Studies: learners examine the causes and effects of misuse of leisure and life skills and values needed for proper use of leisure time\", \"Pre-technical Studies: learners use digital devices to search for information online and make presentations to the class\", \"Creative Arts and Sports: learners write and recite poems on alcohol, drug and substance use/conduct a debate in class\", \"Integrated Science: learners discuss the effects of alcohol, drug and substance use on an individual and the values/life skills needed to avoid the vice\"]',3,'2025-12-07 19:11:31',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35731,8920,'5.4','Wealth, Money and Poverty',8,'[\"discuss Christian teachings on wealth, money and poverty\", \"appraise how the love of money can hinder one from inheriting the Kingdom of God\", \"assess the causes and remedies of poverty in the society today\", \"design ethical ways of acquiring wealth as a youth\", \"desire to acquire wealth through credible ways\"]','[\"in groups read; Deuteronomy 8:18, Ecclesiastes 5:10-19, Proverbs 15:27, Matthew 6:24-27, discuss and make notes\", \"in groups read; Proverbs 14:23, 31:8-9, Luke 3:11, Luke 4:18 on Christian views of poverty and make a presentation using charts or digital devices\", \"read, Matthew 6:19-21, Luke 9:25 & Luke 12:13-21; outline lessons learned and make notes\", \"use the internet or the library to search for information on causes of poverty and remedies; and make a presentation using a chart or a digital device\", \"interview a resource person on how to make money using credible ways as a youth and note key points\", \"in groups brainstorm and come up with business ideas to share with the teacher/parent/guardian; start the business venture, write a report on its progress\", \"write and keep a journal on the progress of the business and share with the teacher/parent/guardian to improve the business based on the feedback provided\"]','[\"Which vices are associated with love for money?\", \"Why is integrity important in terms of money and wealth?\"]','[\"Imagination and Creativity: the skill of reflection is demonstrated as learners implement a business idea, assess its success and improve it based on the feedback provided\", \"Critical thinking and problem-solving skills: the skill of research to find extra information is portrayed as learners use the internet/library to search for information on causes of poverty and the remedies\", \"Digital Literacy: the skill of appropriately selecting digital technology relevant to different tasks is exhibited as learners undertake different tasks and make presentations\"]','[\"Respect: learners understand and appreciate others; they also take turns to air their views and accommodate diverse opinions\", \"Responsibility: learners are answerable as they engage in assigned roles and duties and complete the tasks on time\", \"Unity: learners collaborate with others and share resources amicably\", \"Integrity: learners display fairness, transparency and accountability and apply laid-down procedures in performing various tasks\"]','[\"Self-awareness: learners utilize their talents and abilities as they come up with business ideas and implement the same\", \"Parental Empowerment and Engagement-Resource mobilization and utilization: learners come up with a business idea and share with the teacher/parent/guardian\", \"Group Dynamics: learners work in groups as they debate, brainstorm and discuss various tasks and strategize on how to execute them\", \"Financial Literacy: learners initiate a business enterprise, keep a journal on its progress and improve it based on feedback provided\"]','[\"English: learners communicate effectively as they make presentations and defend their views confidently\", \"Social Studies: learners demonstrate skills such as self-awareness, research skills, good communication and presentation skills, as they perform different tasks/assignments\", \"Pre-technical Studies: learners use digital devices to search for information from the internet and present the findings in class\"]',4,'2025-12-07 19:11:31',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35750,8926,'1.1','Kusikiliza na Kuzungumza: Maamkuzi na Maagano',3,'[\"kutambua maamkuzi na maagano mbalimbali yatumiwayo katika jamii\", \"kutumia ipasavyo maamkuzi na maagano mbalimbali yatumiwayo katika jamii\", \"kuthamini matumizi ya maamkuzi na maagano katika mawasiliano ya kila siku\"]','[\"kutambua maneno yanayotumiwa katika maamkuzi na maagano (k.v. Umeamkaje? Umeshindaje? Safiri salama, mchana mwema, usiku mwema) kutoka kwenye chati, vitabu, kadi maneno, mti maneno, michoro, picha au vifaa vya kidijitali akiwa na wenzake\", \"kujadili na wenzake picha, michoro, video n.k. zinazoonyesha vitendo vya maamkuzi na maagano\", \"kuigiza maamkuzi na maagano akiwa na wenzake ili kujenga umilisi wa kutumia maneno haya\", \"kujadiliana na mzazi au mlezi wake maamkuzi na maagano kutoka kwa jamii yake\"]','[\"Je, unajua maamkuzi na maagano yapi?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anapofanya mazoezi ya maamkuzi pamoja na wenzake.\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapojieleza kwa sauti thabiti anapotoa maagano mbele ya kundi.\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia kifaa cha kidijitali kutazama video za maamkuzi kutoka jamii mbalimbali.\", \"Hamu ya ujifunzaji: mwanafunzi anapotafuta mifano zaidi ya maamkuzi kutoka katika jamii yake na kuwasilisha darasani.\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapowajibu walimu na wenzake kwa maamkuzi yanayofaa.\", \"Uaminifu: mwanafunzi anapozingatia maagano anayofanya na wenzake.\", \"Upendo: mwanafunzi anapowakaribisha wenzake kwa maneno yenye staha.\"]','[\"Uraia: mwanafunzi anapojadili maamkuzi yanayoboresha umoja wa jamii.\", \"Maadili: mwanafunzi anapotambua thamani ya lugha yenye staha katika mahusiano.\"]','[\"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha stadi ya kuwasiliana anayojifunza katika somo la Kiswahili na somo la English Language Activities na Indigenous Language Activities.\", \"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha dhana ya umoja na anayojifunza katika somo la Social Studies.\"]',1,'2025-12-08 07:27:04',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35751,8926,'1.2','Kusoma: Kusoma kwa Ufahamu',3,'[\"kutambua msamiati kuhusu suala lengwa katika kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu\", \"kueleza ujumbe wa kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu\", \"kutabiri kitakachotokea katika kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu\", \"kueleza mafunzo yanayotokana na kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu\", \"kuchangamkia kusoma vifungu vya ufahamu ili kuimarisha stadi ya kusoma\"]','[\"kusoma kifungu chepesi cha maneno 51- 54 na kutambua msamiati wa suala lengwa (k.v. uzalendo, umoja, undugu, ushirikiano, upendo) akiwa na wenzake\", \"kutumia msamiati wa suala lengwa ipasavyo katika mawasiliano\", \"kueleza ujumbe wa kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu akishirikiana na wenzake\", \"kutabiri ujumbe wa kifungu kwa kutazama picha kwenye kitabu, vifaa vya kidijitali au chati akiwa na wenzake\", \"kuthibitisha utabiri wake kuhusu hadithi baada ya kuisoma\", \"kueleza mafunzo yanayotokana na kifungu chepesi cha ufahamu akiwa na wenzake\", \"kumsomea mzazi au mlezi kifungu kuhusu suala lengwa ili amtolee maoni\"]','[\"Je, unapenda kusoma hadithi za aina gani?\", \"Je, ni mambo gani unayoweza kujifunza kutokana na hadithi?\"]','[\"Uwazaji wa kina na utatuzi wa matatizo: mwanafunzi anapochanganua ujumbe wa kifungu na kutoa mafunzo.\", \"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anapozungumza na wenzake kuhusu kifungu alichosoma.\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia kifaa cha kidijitali kusoma hadithi au msamiati mpya.\", \"Hamu ya ujifunzaji: mwanafunzi anapojisomea hadithi zaidi nyumbani ili kuimarisha stadi.\"]','[\"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapofuata mpangilio wa kusoma aliopewa.\", \"Uvumilivu: mwanafunzi anaposoma kifungu kwa makini hadi aelewe ujumbe.\", \"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapowaruhusu wenzake wasome au kueleza maoni yao darasani.\"]','[\"Uraia: mwanafunzi anapojadili hadithi zinazoendeleza uzalendo na undugu.\", \"Elimu ya mazingira: mwanafunzi anaposoma kifungu kinachoeleza namna ya kuhifadhi mazingira yake.\"]','[\"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha ujuzi wa kusoma kwa ufahamu na anayojifunza katika somo la English Language Activities na Indigenous Language Activities.\", \"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha ujumbe wa hadithi unaohusu maadili na somo la Christian Religious Education (CRE) au Islamic Religious Education (IRE).\"]',2,'2025-12-08 07:27:04',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35752,8926,'1.3','Kuandika: Hati Nadhifu: Kifungu',3,'[\"kutambua mambo yanayozingatiwa kufanikisha hati nadhifu\", \"kuandika kifungu cha maneno kati ya 25-30 kwa hati nadhifu\", \"kufurahia kuandika kwa hati nadhifu ili kufanikisha mawasiliano\"]','[\"kutambua mambo mbalimbali yanayozingatiwa kufanikisha hati nadhifu (k.v. muundo wa herufi, nafasi ifaayo kati ya maneno, nafasi zifaazo pambizoni, kutenganisha sentensi ifaavyo, usafi wa nakala) kutoka kwenye kitabu, chati, vifaa vya kidijitali akiwa na wenzake\", \"kunakili kifungu cha maneno yasiyozidi 30 kwa hati nadhifu kutoka kwenye kitabu, chati au vifaa vya kidijitali\", \"kuandika kifungu cha maneno yasiyozidi 30 akizingatia hatua za uandishi (k.v. maandalizi, nakala ya kwanza, urekebishaji, nakala safi) na kuwasomea wenzake\"]','[\"Unazingatia mambo gani unapoandika kifungu?\"]','[\"Uwajibikaji wa kibinafsi: mwanafunzi anapofuata hatua za uandishi hadi kukamilisha nakala safi.\", \"Ubunifu: mwanafunzi anapopanga maneno kwa mtiririko unaovutia akizingatia hati nadhifu.\", \"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anapobadilishana kazi na wenzake kwa ajili ya maoni.\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia kifaa cha kidijitali kuiga mwandiko au kuhariri kazi yake.\"]','[\"Usafi: mwanafunzi anaposomeka vizuri kwa kuzingatia hati nadhifu.\", \"Uvumilivu: mwanafunzi anapojirekebisha mara kadhaa hadi afikie kiwango kinachotarajiwa.\", \"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapokubali mrejesho kutoka kwa walimu na wenzake.\"]','[\"Maadili: mwanafunzi anapojifunza kuwa mwangalifu na mpole katika uandishi.\", \"Ubunifu na uvumbuzi: mwanafunzi anapotengeneza kadi au kifungu kinachoonyesha dhamira ya uzalendo.\"]','[\"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha hati nadhifu anayojifunza katika somo la Kiswahili na inavyohitajika katika somo la English Language Activities na Indigenous Language Activities.\", \"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha maudhui ya uzalendo na somo la Social Studies.\"]',3,'2025-12-08 07:27:04',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35753,8926,'1.4','Sarufi: Matumizi ya Yeye na Wao',3,'[\"kutambua neno yeye na wao katika sentensi\", \"kutumia neno yeye na wao ipasavyo katika sentensi\", \"kufurahia kutumia neno yeye na wao katika mawasiliano\"]','[\"kusikiliza kifungu au wimbo unaohusu yeye na wao kutoka kwa mwalimu au kifaa cha kidijitali\", \"kutambua neno yeye na wao kutoka kifungu alichokisikiliza\", \"kusoma vifungu na kutambua neno yeye na wao akiwa na wenzake au katika kikundi\", \"kujaza nafasi kwa kutumia yeye na wao\", \"kutumia yeye na wao katika kuigiza mazungumzo na wenzake katika kikundi (k.v.Yeye anasoma - wao wanasoma)\"]','[\"Ni maneno gani unayoyatumia kuwataja wenzako bila kutumia majina yao halisi?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake katika kutunga sentensi kwa kutumia yeye na wao.\", \"Uwazaji wa kina: mwanafunzi anapotofautisha matumizi ya nafsi ya umoja na wingi katika sentensi.\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia kifaa cha kidijitali kusikiliza kifungu chenye viwakilishi hivi.\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapowasilisha sentensi zake mbele ya darasa.\"]','[\"Heshima: mwanafunzi anapotumia viwakilishi vinavyofaa kuwatambua watu wengine.\", \"Uwajibikaji: mwanafunzi anapofuata maagizo ya kazi anapotumia yeye na wao.\", \"Umoja: mwanafunzi anapofanya kazi ya kikundi bila kubeza michango ya wengine.\"]','[\"Uraia: mwanafunzi anapojadili watu mashuhuri wa taifa kwa kutumia viwakilishi sahihi.\", \"Elimu ya kijamii: mwanafunzi anapotumia sentensi kuelezea tabia njema za wana jamii.\"]','[\"Mwanafunzi anaweza kuhusisha dhana ya viwakilishi na anayojifunza katika somo la English Language Activities na Indigenous Language Activities.\", \"Mwanafunzi anaweza kutumia sentensi hizo kuelezea masomo mengine kama Environmental Activities au Religious Education.\"]',4,'2025-12-08 07:27:04',NULL,NULL,NULL),(35754,8927,'2.1','Kusikiliza na Kuzungumza: Matamshi Bora: Vokali na Konsonanti za Kiswahili',3,'[\"kutambua vokali za Kiswahili katika matini\", \"kutamka ipasavyo vokali za Kiswahili katika matini\", \"kutambua konsonanti za Kiswahili katika matini\", \"kutamka ipasavyo konsonanti za Kiswahili katika matini\", \"kuchangamkia kutamka sauti za Kiswahili ili kuboresha matamshi\"]','[\"kutambua vokali za Kiswahili katika matini ya kutamkwa au kuandikwa\", \"kutamka ipasavyo vokali za Kiswahili\", \"kutambua konsonanti za Kiswahili katika matini ya kutamkwa au kuandikwa\", \"kutamka ipasavyo konsonanti za Kiswahili\", \"kusikiliza vokali na konsonanti za Kiswahili (a, b, ch, d, dh, e, f, g, gh, h, i, j, k, l, m, n, ng, ng’, ny, o, p, r, s, sh, t, th, u, v, w, y, z) zikitamkwa na mwalimu, mgeni mwalikwa au vifaa vya kidijitali na kutambua vokali na konsonanti\", \"kutambua vokali na konsonanti za Kiswahili katika kifungu kikisomwa na mwalimu, mgeni mwalikwa au kwenye vifaa vya kidijitali akiwa na wenzake\", \"kutamka maneno, sentensi au kifungu chenye sauti za Kiswahili akiwa na wenzake\", \"kujirekodi akitamka sauti za Kiswahili akitumia vifaa vya kidijitali na kujitathmini pamoja au kutathminiwa na wenzake\", \"kutamka sauti za kiswahili ipasavyo naye mzazi au mlezi ampe maoni yake\"]','[\"Je, kwa nini ni muhimu kutambua sauti za lugha fulani?\"]','[\"Mawasiliano na ushirikiano: mwanafunzi anaposhirikiana na wenzake kutamka vokali na konsonanti mbalimbali.\", \"Kujiamini: mwanafunzi anapojieleza kwa sauti thabiti akifanya mazoezi ya matamshi bora.\", \"Ujuzi wa kidijitali: mwanafunzi anapotumia kifaa cha kidijitali kurekodi na kutathmini matamshi yake.\", \"Hamu ya ujifunzaji: mwanafun